data.description: Picky people pay attention! This is the one you've been waiting for! This home is stunning and it's located at the end of a cul-de-sac. It's in ever popular Elgin school district. It's also 5 minutes to Apache Gate, 5 minutes to trendy Medicine Park, less than 5 minutes to beautiful Lake Lawtonka, 10 minutes to Lawton and barely 5 minutes to the wildlife refuge. This home will not disappoint and has lots of storage with walk-in closets, walk-in pantry, cabinets galore, hall tree in utility room and floored attic. The huge back porch and uninterrupted mountain sunsets will help you relax each evening. The seller has added a storm shelter to make you feel more confident during storm season. The large living area is completely open to the kitchen. Wonderful full picture windows line the back of the living area and all windows are covered with upscale remote blinds. The bedrooms are amazingly spacious so you and the kids will have plenty of room. Call the Munchel Team today with questions or to schedule your private showing.
